            <description><![CDATA[【别生闷气！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E6%98%93%E5%BE%97%E7%94%B2%E7%8A%B6%E8%85%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E6%8A%91%E9%83%81%E6%98%93%E5%BE%97%E7%94%B2%E7%8A%B6%E8%85%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#女性情绪抑郁易得甲状腺疾病#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[awsl]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a3awsl-ed1a33c1b3.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】甲状腺疾病以女性偏多，专家提醒，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%94%B2%E7%8A%B6%E8%85%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%8E%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A730%E5%B2%81%E5%88%B060%E5%B2%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%94%B2%E7%8A%B6%E8%85%BA%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%E5%A4%9A%E5%8F%91%E4%BA%8E%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A730%E5%B2%81%E5%88%B060%E5%B2%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#甲状腺疾病多发于女性30岁到60岁#</span></a>。女性患上甲状腺疾病一是在情绪抑郁的时候，二是在青春发育期，第三是在孕期或产后六个月以内，最后是更年期。一些年轻女性在怀孕以后，出现了流产或胎停的情况，这和很多因素有关，甲状腺在其中占了一席之地，并且产生了很大的不良影响。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4885738907697241" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视网的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://wx1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/003z5L7fly1hck8hit5c0j61hc0u0q5k02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/2Q3LLPW6lx084khe6uWI01041200zPiR0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680844757&amp;ssig=%2BsNqsXv1CB&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/Aui64aBNlx084khewccg01041200hHf10E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680844757&amp;ssig=VaOTsr7TZV&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://locallimit.us.sinaimg.cn/o0/NFtPXtAJlx084khdoeZy01041200bnjy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1680844757&amp;ssig=wbtxeOuZ2O&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4885738907697241&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
